dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Goodhue County, Minnesota, C-12, Part B, Plate 7, Bedrock and Water-Table Hydrogeology
dc_description_s: Maps showing ground water resources and aquifer characteristics in the bedrock and unconsolidated sediments overlying the bedrock, including the age of the water as determined from radioactive isotopes in the water, scale 1:150,000, Goodhue County.
dc_publisher_s: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters
